think-about-penguins.adventure.craig.mayhew.io.	300	IN	TXT	"As you stare into the distance you remember the ridiculous gait of a lone penguin. It's said that it is biologically impossible to be unhappy while watching a penguin attempt to waddle from A to B.  (^v^)  <( )>   w wYou imagine one walking into the office, clocking in, and taking a seat.As you imagine a penguin furiously slapping a keyboard, you are reminded of the matter at hand...go ask-what-did-you-do to see if anyone will give you at least a half truthful answer."
water-plant.adventure.craig.mayhew.io.	300	IN	TXT	"You fill a cup of water from the office water cooler and once back at your desk, you pour some into the plant pot.The plant pot is terracotta and even after all this time, remains uncracked. Few people realise that most plants reproduce via mitosis. Each new plant being a near facsimile of the parent.No one has any idea that the private key of your bitcoin wallet is encoded into the plant's junk DNA. Each time you gift someone a cutting, they are unwittingly providing you with an offsite backup.Anyway, better get back to what you were doing..."
